*qemu-kvm-0.13.0-r1 (02 Nov 2010)

  02 Nov 2010; Jorge Manuel B. S. Vicetto <jmbsvicetto@gentoo.org>
  -files/qemu-kvm-0.12.1-kvm_save_mpstate-workaround.patch,
